Louis van Gaal was snapped with Manchester City women 's players Toni Duggan and Isobel Christiansen in a restaurant .
Duggan uploaded a photograph on Instagram of her , Christiansen and Everton 's Michelle Hinnigan at Wing 's Chinese restaurant following United 's 4-2 win against City .
Winggan has removed the photo from Instagram and issued an apology on Facebook .
Van Gaal was at the restaurant for the derby .